</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-CLICK-FOR-HEALTH-VIDEOS-SCI-NYTSF </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
PLAY TWO VIDEO GAMES AND CALL ME IN THE MORNING  
 
</HEADLINE>
   (This 525-word ``separate buy'' article is from TECHNOLOGY REVIEW
magazine.  
  
