u a &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-YANKS-CLEMENS-REVIEW-     02-20 0522
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-YANKS-CLEMENS-REVIEW-NYT </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
BASEBALL'S GREATEST TEAM GETS A PITCHER TO MATCH 
</HEADLINE>
  (The Week in Review) 
(DUPLICATION WARNING: also sent with `s' code) 
(NOTE TO INTERNATIONAL CLIENTS: For international clients' use by
special arrangement only. Asian and European points: contact Karl
Horwitz in Paris for details and prices (Phone: 47 42 17 11; FAX:
47-42-80-44). Latin American points: contact Olivia Vasquez in Los
Angeles (Phone: 310-996-0075; FAX: 310-996-0089) 
(bl) 
 By ALLEN BARRA   
 c.1999 N.Y. Times News Service    
<TEXT>
<P>
   NEW YORK _ The story is that when David Wells first came here
from Baltimore, he wanted to wear Babe Ruth's No. 3. They had to
explain to him that the number was retired; he settled for wearing
one of Ruth's old caps.
</P>
