</P>
<P>
   HUNTING-TURKEYS _ Turkey season is still a month away, but
hunters must do their scouting in order to get a gobbler. Two
experts, Roscoe Reams and Jan Chase, dispense advice on pre-season
scouting. Roscoe, 74, is a long-time, very successful, legendary
hunter. Jan, 46, has accomplished turkey hunting's ``world slam''
in under a year, one of the fastest completions on record. It's age
and experience vs. female intuition. (Mitchell, Atlanta
Journal-Constitution). MOVED
